The '''Karap Valley''' was a depression on [[Hewl]]. It was characterized by its frequent fog banks.

The [[Filar-Nitzan/Legends|Filar-Nitzan]] [[Spy/Legends|spy]] [[Vacander]], a gaseous being, could hide in the fog banks of the valley. While doing so, he found [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] Colonel [[Palpatine Essex Yerac|P. Essex Yerac]] chasing a group of [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]]. Vacander showed Yerac his red [[Eye/Legends|eyes]], apparently coming from the fog itself, and ordered Yerac to keep distances.

